-- Garden Controller v5.23
-- Changes vs v5.22:
--   1. Plant Rush: completely rewritten auto-aim loop
--      - 0.2s scan interval for fast enemy tracking
--      - Priority tier logic: Small > Medium > Tough > Boss
--      - Auto-equips TomatoShooter from backpack when enemies detected
--      - After equip: forces camera zoom-out (CameraMinZoomDistance trick)
--        so the game doesn't snap to first-person view
--      - Auto-aim only (no FireServer) — TomatoShooter fires automatically
--        when the reticle is on target
--      - Velocity lead prediction (0.1s) for moving enemies
--   2. Removed old AutoShoot / FireServer / ShootEvent logic from Plant Rush
--   3. Floor 1 Auto Fertilize fix retained from v5.22

